p: The inflammatory responses of AG129 mice were also observed following infections with 10 2 PFU of the M-30 and S-27 viruses ( Figure 7). Cytokine levels in the brains and spleens (except IL-10 ( p = 0.0317) in the spleens) were not significantly different between M-30- and S-27-infected mice ( Figure 7A,B).
